OL,4,CCovid: Fraud reports in Wales up by 25%
OL,5,Cduring pandemic
OL,6, Fraud reports in Wales have increased
OL,7, by more than 25% since the start of the
OL,8, Covid pandemic, figures have shown.
OL,10,FData from Action Fraud showed there
OL,11,Fwere a total of 18,061 reports of fraud
OL,12,Fin Wales from April 2020 to March 2021,
OL,13,Fup from 14,277 in the previous year.
OL,15,FBBC Wales has spoken to people who said
OL,16,Fthey noticed an increase in cold calls
OL,17,Ffrom phone numbers almost identical to
OL,18,Ftheir own.
OL,20,FTrading Standards has warned people not
OL,21,Fto click on links in text messages.
